						<section id="Playstyle">
							<h2>Protection Paladin Playstyle in The War Within Season 2</h2>

							<p>
								Protection Paladin operates on a priority list with a Combo Point-style resource system.
								This means that all of your actions will be used in an order of highest value with each GCD,
								meaning that you will need to judge your current state throughout an encounter and make some predictions.
								We tend to follow 5 key rules:
							</p>

							<div class="guide-container">
								<div class="guide-row">
									<div class="icon-slot"></div>
									<div class="guide-text">
										<strong>Never overcap and waste Holy Power:</strong> Holy Power is a critical resource that helps our damage, mitigation, and healing. We don't want to waste any!
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="guide-row">
									<div class="icon-slot"></div>
									<div class="guide-text">
										<strong>Generate resources:</strong> Use <span class="ability">Hammer of Wrath</span>, <span class="ability">Judgment</span>, and <span class="ability">Blessed Hammer</span> to build Holy Power.
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="guide-row">
									<div class="icon-slot"></div>
									<div class="guide-text">
										<strong>Smooth damage intake:</strong> Use <span class="ability">Shield of the Righteous</span> when you have 3–5 Holy Power. This is your primary resource spender and should be your default option when you want to spend Holy Power.
									</div>
								</div>

