						<section id="addons">
							<h2>WeakAuras (WA) & Addons</h2>

							<h3>Recommended WeakAuras</h3>

							<ul>
								<li><strong>Shield of the Righteous Tracker</strong> - Tracks active uptime and expiration for Shield of the Righteous so you can keep near 100% armor buff uptime.</li>
								<li><strong>Avenger’s Shield Cooldown</strong> - Makes it very clear when Avenger’s Shield is ready to fire again. Essential for Holy Power flow and interrupting key abilities.</li>
								<li><strong>Consecration Tracker</strong> - Reminds you when you have moved out of Consecration or if it expires naturally. Keeps you inside it for passive Mastery mitigation bonuses.</li>
								<li><strong>Shining Light Tracker</strong> - Shows stacks for Shining Light procs (free Word of Glory casts) so you don’t waste them by accident.</li>
								<li><strong>Eye of Tyr Cooldown</strong> - Tracks Eye of Tyr separately, so you know exactly when you can pop it for AoE mitigation during big pulls.</li>
								<li><strong>Word of Glory Emergency Warning</strong> - Flashes a warning when your HP drops below a certain threshold and you have Holy Power to heal yourself.</li>
							</ul>

							<h3>Recommended Addons</h3>

							<ul>
								<li><strong>Details!</strong> - Advanced Damage Meter addon. Use it with Tank Plugins activated to show defensive uptime (Shield of the Righteous, Ardent Defender usage, etc.). Helps you audit your cooldown usage.</li>
								<li><strong>BigWigs or DBM</strong> - Boss mod addons. Provide timers for incoming raid/dungeon mechanics. Absolutely necessary for planning your cooldown usage during heavy damage phases.</li>
								<li><strong>Plater</strong> - Highly customizable nameplate addon. Can show when mobs are casting dangerous interrupts or when targets are ignoring threat. Very helpful for tanking large groups.</li>
								<li><strong>OmniCD</strong> - Tracks party/raid cooldowns. Know when your healers have external cooldowns ready or when other players can battle res.</li>
								<li><strong>Method Raid Tools</strong> - Great overall raid helper with cooldown tracking, battle res timers, and other protection utilities.</li>
								<li><strong>WeakAuras Companion App</strong> - Not an in-game addon, but used outside the game to update your WeakAuras library easily without redownloading them manually.</li>
							</ul>

						</section>
